{"tid":2267288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英情報機關招募中文專家","createTime":"2020-11-02T03:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T04:05:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"417ba622becf8e464dbbed1b93610f251ecf9d81","tid":2267288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201102/O3TJAXXPHJB4NJRQKHUO2BJQSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201102%2FO3TJAXXPHJB4NJRQKHUO2BJQSY%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxcyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=e6aa9c7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201102%2FO3TJAXXPHJB4NJRQKHUO2BJQSY%2F&h=e783dc02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201102/O3TJAXXPHJB4NJRQKHUO2BJQSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英情報機關招募中文專家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1dulZSq4Vr7HiSd1nsAzYv4-Hl0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CSTZKNE5XNEANA7INMRGWQKUHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1dulZSq4Vr7HiSd1nsAzYv4-Hl0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCSTZKNE5XNEANA7INMRGWQKUHQ.jpg&h=bc6d8341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■麥卡勒姆稱中國威脅漸趨嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n中國間諜問題引起歐洲情報機構警惕。英國《標準晚報》日前報道，英國軍情五處（MI5）、軍情六處（MI6）和政府通信總部（GCHQ）即將展開活動，加強招募懂中文的語言專家加入「情報調查的核心」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應對中國間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n一些求職網站已刊登了英國情報機構的招聘廣告，內容寫：「即將公開：MI5、MI6和GCHQ近期內將展開中文語言專家招聘活動。」廣告稱，MI5的中文語言專家將提供情報分析，在指導項目和推動調查中發揮積極作用，但不會指揮及引導情報調查。<br />\n<br />\n英國軍情五處新處長麥卡勒姆在上月14日表示，來自中國、俄羅斯與伊朗等方面的間諜與干擾行動變得越來越嚴重和複雜。。。。。。。。。。。。。他透露，軍情五處將謹慎且優先應對中國的活動。<br />\n<br />\n北京的間諜活動通常是針對敏感商業資訊及知識產權，。。。。。。。。。。。有英國媒體報道，英國計劃修改針對外國間諜代理人在英活動的法律，將對外國間諜代理人的刑罰產生重大影響。<br />\n<br />\n《標準晚報》"},{"pid":"5753b811e6400ff6ccf27f68d3a9ab2225507c5a","tid":2267288,"uid":228995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"應對中國間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n最後會唔會招募左間諜？"},{"pid":"eda88240a798d9f08742631a92ad47bbeb4ed327","tid":2267288,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"為祖國盡忠既時候到了"},{"pid":"e4d110ff35326b87a55c4e6c0f69397f6144a349","tid":2267288,"uid":366652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5753b811e6400ff6ccf27f68d3a9ab2225507c5a","tid":2267288,"uid":228995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"應對中國間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n最後會唔會招募左間諜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"都好<br />\n用嚟玩反間計"},{"pid":"ac4c7edc19b98de12ae07ae5bd8e944fc4335d95","tid":2267288,"uid":357710,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5753b811e6400ff6ccf27f68d3a9ab2225507c5a","tid":2267288,"uid":228995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"應對中國間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n最後會唔會招募左間諜？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:37:27.000Z","msg":"yeah , 連登仔去應徵同英國說很安全，再recap番自己去年活動照片interview証明可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1ce02960e7d7aaf09ceefdfbb3b5e8515c0156","tid":2267288,"uid":247048,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5753b811e6400ff6ccf27f68d3a9ab2225507c5a","tid":2267288,"uid":228995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"應對中國間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n最後會唔會招募左間諜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"要中文專家，但無話要華人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591982fe55e936f9fc0035e65cd25cad26dd7710","tid":2267288,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5753b811e6400ff6ccf27f68d3a9ab2225507c5a","tid":2267288,"uid":228995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"應對中國間諜活動<br />\n<br />\n最後會唔會招